    "Political Bias: we reserve all articles from either all 'Left'-or 'Right'-biased publishers for testing, and train on articles from the opposite political bias, along with any 'Center'-biased publishers 6.",
    "Misinformation Type: similarly, we reserve all articles from either all 'Questionable Source' or 'Conspiracy-Pseudoscience' publishers for testing, and train on articles from the other misinformation class.",
    "We use an i.i.d.",
    "split of reliable articles to ensure a similar class distribution in all splits",
    "We include a substantially expanded description of each split's construction in Appendix C. In the 'Topic' and 'Publisher' splits were constructed by sampling from the smallest topics and publishers."
